 the twentieth century, and anticipating what is to come.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aMotion picturesxProduction and directionxHistory. 7aART / Film & Video.2bisacsh  a20th century.  aabstraction.  aart forms.  acinema.  acomprehensive history.  adeteriorating film.  aexperimental film.  afilm strips.  ahandmade cinema.  ahistory of cinema.  aintersection of art and media.  akinetic art.  amedia.  amovies.  amoving image artists.  apainted film.  apainting and scratching.  aproduction.  apsychedelic light shows.  ashadow history.  asignificance of the moving image.  aunconventional filmmaking practices.  avideo synthesis.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertArt and Architecture eBook-Package 2020z978311073823008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2020z9783110704655oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2020 Englishz978311070478508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069041540uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520972582zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520972582423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520972582.jpg  a978-3-11-069041-5  UC Press Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070478-5  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-073823-0  Art and Architecture eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  